title: THE VAMPIRE DIARIES 005 (2013) (DC) (Digital) (Pirate-Empire)
description:
The Vampire Diaries #5

"Home for the Holidays" part 1 of 2!

When Stefan makes a clandestine Christmas visit to Mystic Falls, his battles against an unexpected group of vampires distract him from the town's Winter Party and the teen blowout in the woods.

Written by B. Clay Moore
Art by Tony Shasteen
Cover by Cat Staggs

Published by DC Comics
23 Pages
Digital Release Date: December 26, 2013
Age Rating: 15+ Only
Genres: Movies and TV, Supernatural/Occult, Vampires, Werewolves
